If they move too quick

303
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:19,810
(Oh whey oh)

304
00:22:19,810 --> 00:22:21,890
They're falling down like a domino.

305
00:22:22,130 --> 00:22:24,420
All the bazaar men by the Nile

306
00:22:24,470 --> 00:22:26,540
They got the money on a bet

307
00:22:26,790 --> 00:22:28,140
Gold crocodiles

308
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,040
(Oh whey oh)

309
00:22:29,050 --> 00:22:31,160
They snap their teeth on your cigarette

310
00:22:31,460 --> 00:22:33,660
Foreign types with their hookah pipes say

311
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:39,630
(Way oh way oh, ooh way oh way oh)

312
00:22:40,690 --> 00:22:42,870
Walk like an Egyptian

313
00:22:54,610 --> 00:22:57,080
The blond waitresses take their trays

314
00:22:57,110 --> 00:22:59,150
They spin around and they cross the floor

315
00:22:59,420 --> 00:23:00,740
They've got the moves

316
00:23:00,740 --> 00:23:01,720
(Oh whey oh)

317
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,800
You drop your drink then they bring you more

318
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:06,430
All the school kids so sick of books

319
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:08,590
They like the punk and the metal band

320
00:23:08,750 --> 00:23:10,040
When the buzzer rings

321
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:11,040
(Oh whey oh)

322
00:23:11,060 --> 00:23:13,210
They're walking like an Egyptian

323
00:23:13,390 --> 00:23:15,480
All the kids in the marketplace say

324
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:21,980
(Ay oh whey oh, ay oh whey oh)

325
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:25,130
Walk like an Egyptian.

326
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:29,420
这艘船是怎么回事

327
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:33,090
舷梯放下来了 为什么一个人也没看到

328
00:23:33,130 --> 00:23:34,640
完全没有人迹

329
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,630
泡过海水黏乎乎的

330
00:23:36,730 --> 00:23:38,330
这就是所谓的…

331
